{"tid":911914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"D&G被轟辱華網購平台下架 外交部：不希望升為外交問題","createTime":"2018-11-22T09:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T09:33:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd8f3e75b51c29c021a88969e4803fb6bc29228","tid":911914,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】意大利時裝品牌杜嘉班納Dolce &amp; Gabbana（D&amp;G）辱華風波進一步擴大，受到大批内地網民批評，原定昨晚在上海舉行的大型時裝秀，最終遭到中國演藝人抵制而取消。而內地多個網購平台，包括天貓及京東等，都已將D&amp;G產品下架。<br />\n北京外交部發言人耿爽回應意大利記者時表示，中方不希望此事上升為外交問題，但外界應了解中國民眾如何看待這一問題。耿爽稱，此事本質上不是外交問題，中方也不希望其上升為外交問題，與其來問外交部發言人，不如去問一問中國的普通民眾，看他們如何看待這個問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/d-g%E8%A2%AB%E8%BD%9F%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%8D%87%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-084000790.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fd-g%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25BD%259F%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%259E%25B6-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-084000790.html&d=%2FXlLKxHMo%2FigLamPEfJo7P755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bbf51c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/d-g%E8%A2%AB%E8%BD%9F%E8%BE%B1%E8%8F%AF%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%8D%87%E7%82%BA%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-084000790.html</a>"},{"pid":"c581c87311aaac3512d89525f8f8eefbe71ba263","tid":911914,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"口交部：你班柒頭做乜又撩多個國家呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9f39e3dd3d66a0ec488d87170ab04671b72035","tid":911914,"uid":10757,"like":0,"di